{"authors":"王超","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>各地安全","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\">\n   <st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"8\" month=\"1\" year=\"2018\">\n    <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">8</font><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">日</span></span></span></span>\n   </st1:chsdate><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">，黑龙江煤矿安监局召开<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2018</font><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">年度第<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">次监察执法工作视频例会，听取机关有关业务处室、中心和各监察分局（站）工作汇报，安排部署<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">月份重点工作任务。党组成员、副局长张瑞庭出席会议并就近期重点工作提出要求。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </font><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">张瑞庭指出，<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2017</font><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">年是极不平凡的一年，尽管煤监系统工作任务异常繁重，责任压力异常紧迫，但全局上下特别是一线监察人员工作热情高涨，工作措施务实有力，突出实干担当和正确的选人用人导向，以上率下，形成头雁效应。各单位各部门抓基础强管理，抓执法强效能，抓服务强形象，抓廉政强纪律，全局上下洋溢着风清气正、锐意进取、干事创业的良好氛围。局机关各处室围绕中心、服务大局，与分局（站）上下呼应、见缝插针，最大限度地形成了合力。<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2017</font><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">年全省煤矿死亡事故起数和人数同比减幅<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">41.67%</font><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">和<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">21.95%</font><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">张瑞庭分析了当前黑龙江煤矿现状和存在的突出问题。他强调，黑龙江省煤矿多、井型小、灾害重、事故多，工作难度大，面对诸多需要攻克的难题，新的一年不但要有新思路、新目标，还要有新气象、新作为。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">就全面做好<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">1</font><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">月份工作，张瑞庭要求，一是要认真学习贯彻习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想和党的十九大精神。要按照局党组的要求和机关党委安排部署，切实将学习党的十九大精神作为当前和今后一个时期的首要政治任务。要牢固树立党的一切工作到支部的鲜明导向，真正把功夫下在支部，持续发挥支部学习教育的主体作用，进一步激发支部学习教育主要平台的活力。要按时参加网络培训，通过认真学、反复学、深入学，切实达到武装头脑、指导实践、推动工作的目的。</span></span></span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">二是要谋划好全年工作。围绕班子和队伍建设、作风建设、廉政建设和执法监察工作，深入研究、思考谋划全年的目标任务、工作思路和制度措施，推动安全监察和安全生产工作再上水平。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">三是要做好岁末年初的各项监察工作。面对岁末年初煤炭价格上扬，煤矿企业生产欲望强烈，超能力生产、非法生产等问题可能增加的实际，要加强对重点县区、重点煤矿的执法力度，以前一段检查发现问题的整改为切入点，对问题和隐患抓住不放、一盯到底，确保整改到位。要运用各种监察形式，坚持“零点”行动，加大夜查巡查力度，打好“组合拳”，严厉打击非法违法生产行为。要加大对县区政府的监督指导力度，对于存在问题较多的，必须严肃约谈，做到早提醒、真督查、严执法，确保岁末年初全省煤矿安全生产形势稳定。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">四是要坚持从严执法不放松。必须有为了遏制重特大事故敢为天下先的情怀，摁住事故才是硬道理，要想摁住事故，只有从严执法，才能能倒逼企业主体责任的落实、地方安全监管的强化、重大灾害的治理、安全基础管理的加强。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">五是要严格执行“八项规定”和廉洁自律各项要求。要强化纪律意识、规矩意识，自觉抵制消极腐败因素的诱惑侵蚀，做到廉洁履职，廉洁用权，廉洁做人。要严防利益陷阱，做好自我防范，不给任何人可乘之机。要严格执行中央八项规定精神，立足于早、着眼于小，抓常抓细、久久为功，严防“四风”反弹，使严实守规成为日常的思想自觉。</span></p> <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 12pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">会上，党组成员、纪检组长刘学东，党组成员、副局长王永华分别对有关工作进行安排部署，提出明确要求。副巡视员雷景学主持会议，并就贯彻会议精神提出具体意见。</span></p><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\">局机关各处室副处级以上干部、事业单位主要负责人，各监察分局（站）全体监察人员在主、分会场参加会议。<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;\"> </span></span></font>\n</div>","createTime":1518425397183,"modules":[],"pubSource":"黑龙江煤矿安监局","pubTime":1515600000000,"region":["黑龙江省"],"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"黑龙江煤矿安监局召开2018年第一次监察执法工作视频例会","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5517/2018/0111/300896/content_300896.htm"}
{"authors":"杨宇虹","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>基础管理","content":"<td class=\"font14 lineHeight25\" id=\"artibody\"><font face=\"宋体\"> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">国家煤矿安监局办公室关于征求</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt\">\n     <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \r\n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /-->\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">《煤矿安全生产标准化考核定级办法</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">（征求意见稿）》意见的函</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">煤安监司函办〔<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016〕<span lang=\"EN-US\">31号<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">各产煤省、自治区、直辖市及新疆生产建设兵团煤矿安全质量标准化工作主管部门：</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">国家煤矿安监局在《煤矿安全质量标准化考核评级办法（试行）》基础上，拟定了《煤矿安全生产标准化考核定级办法（征求意见稿）》，现征求你单位意见（可从国家安全监管总局网站“征求意见”栏目下载，网址：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">www.chinasafety.gov.cn</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">）。请认真组织研究，并于<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2016</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">11</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">18</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日前将书面意见连同电子版一并反馈国家煤矿安监局行业管理司。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">联系人及电话：梁子荣，<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">010-64464789</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">、<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">64464294</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">（传真）；电子信箱：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">liangzr@chinasafety.gov.cn</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">。</span></span></span></span></span><