{"authors":"杨宇虹","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>重要通知","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">国家煤矿安监局办公室关于召开</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">第十七届国际煤层气暨页岩气研讨会的通知</span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">各有关单位：<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">定于<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2017</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">11</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月下旬在河南省平顶山市召开第十七届国际煤层气暨页岩气研讨会，现将有关事项通知如下：<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n         <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">一、会议内容<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">研讨深部矿井瓦斯灾害防治关键技术、煤矿瓦斯抽采与利用技术、采煤采气一体化开发技术、井上下联合抽采瓦斯综合防治技术；交流煤层气勘探开发关键技术；探讨废弃煤矿瓦斯开发利用、煤矿通风瓦斯利用及页岩气开发利用产业相关政策；交流煤层气开发国际成功经验。<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">二、会议时间和地点<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">会议时间：<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">11</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">28</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日至<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">29</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-