{"authors":"杨宇虹","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>安全分析与事故通报","content":"<td class=\"font11pt lineHeight25\" id=\"artibody\"><font face=\"宋体\"> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">一、重大事故情况<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">重大事故发生<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">起，死亡<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">12</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人。</span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">3</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">6</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">10</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">时<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">53</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">分，吉林白山市江源县，吉煤集团通化矿业公司松树镇煤矿发生煤与瓦斯突出事故，造成<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">12</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人死亡、<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">7</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人受伤。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21.1pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">二、上周煤矿安全生产主要特点及警示<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">上周煤矿发生重大事故且总量环比上升。上周煤矿事故发生<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">6</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">起、死亡<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">20</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人，环比增加<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">4</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">起、<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">18</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">人，且发生<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">起重大事故。暴露出煤矿在复工复产过程中隐患排查不到位、四位一体防突措施不落实等问题。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">防范措施：一是切实落实煤矿企业主体责任，扎实做好煤矿隐患排查治理工作；二是加大复工复产期间煤矿监管监察力度，督促企业制定并严格执行复产安全检查方案，防范复产期间煤矿发生重特大事故。</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <o:p>\n     <font face=\"Calibri\">&nbsp;</font>\n    </o:p></span></p></font></td>","createTime":1518425397138,"modules":[],"pubSource":"安全监管总局统计司","pubTime":1457280000000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"2016年2月29日－3月6日煤矿安全生产简要情况","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_21857/2016/0329/266827/content_266827.htm"}
