NT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">安监总煤行〔<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016〕<span lang=\"EN-US\">79号<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">各产煤省、自治区、直辖市及新疆生产建设兵团煤炭行业管理部门、煤矿安全监管部门，各省级煤矿安全监察局，司法部直属煤矿管理局，有关中央企业：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">按照《煤矿安全质量标准化考核评级办法（试行）》和《煤矿安全质量标准化基本要求及评分方法（试行）》<span lang=\"EN-US\">(<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">煤安监行管〔<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">〕<span lang=\"EN-US\">1<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">号<span lang=\"EN-US\">)<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">规定，经对各地区申报的一级安全质量标准化煤矿进行资料审查、现场抽查、网上公示，确定<span lang=\"EN-US\">2015<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年度一级安全质量标准化煤矿<span lang=\"EN-US\">789<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">处（名单附后），现予公布。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><a href=\"files_founder_1337228032/141721557.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">附件：<span lang=\"EN-US\">2015<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年度一级安全质量标准化煤矿名单</span></span></span></p></a> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"right\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <o:p>\n     &nbsp;\n    </o:p></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">国家安全监管总局<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">国家煤矿安监局<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=\"right\">\n   <st1:chsdate year=\"2016\" month=\"7\" day=\"21\" islunardate=\"False\" isrocdate=\"False\" w:st=\"on\">\n    <span lang=\"EN-US\">2016<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\">7<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\">21<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">日</span></span></span></span></span></span>\n   </st1:chsdate></p><font face=\"宋体\"></font></span></td>","createTime":1518425397664,"modules":[],"pubSource":"安全监管总局办公厅","pubTime":1469116800000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"国家安全监管总局","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5476/2016/0722/273300/content_273300.htm"}
{"authors":"王超","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>各地安全","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> </font> \n <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 16pt;\">2018<span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">年，福建煤监局将进一步巩固煤矿全面安全“体检”成果，在全面总结煤矿全面安全“体检”工作的经验和做法的基础上，结合安全生产大检查、风险隐患排查大排查大整治等活动开展“回头看”。并重点检查煤矿企业按照“五落实”要求的整改落实情况，对事故隐患和问题突出的煤矿加大“回头看”检查频度。<span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"> </span></span></span></p>\n <font face=\"宋体\"></font> \n <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">深化煤矿安全生产大检查，重点对照国务院安委办督导组、综合督查组督查时发现的问题和隐患，同时分析煤矿大检查中发现的突出问题，督促煤矿开展全面彻底的自查自改。同时，加强对列入淘汰关闭退出、长期停产等矿井的巡查监管和检查，对明停暗开、“死灰复燃”、突击生产等违法生产行为，坚决从严查处、从严问责。<span style=\"font-size: 16pt;\"> </span></span></p>\n <font face=\"宋体\"></font> \n <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; line-height: 28pt; text-indent: 32pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-hansi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">加强煤矿水害防治工作，积极探索“九大专项整治工程”涉及煤矿安全整治的有效办法，督促煤矿健全水害防治责任体系，构建水害防治长效机制，完善水害防治各项制度，对有水害威胁的矿井做到“三专两探一撤”；严格落实《煤矿防治水规定》及各项防治水措施，强化现场管理，及时消除各类水害隐患；加强安全教育培训，促进煤矿井下作业人员具备必要的防治水知识，掌握井下透水征兆，熟悉避水灾路线；落实生产现场带班人员、班组长和调度人员直接处置权和指挥权，发现透水征兆，必须停工停产撤人，杜绝冒险作业。</span></p>\n <font face=\"宋体\"></font>\n</div>","createTime":1518425397680,"modules":[],"pubSource":"福建煤监局","pubTime":1516204800000,"region":["福建省"],"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"福建煤监局将开展“回头看 深入推动煤矿安全大检查","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5517/2018/0118/300899/content_300899.htm"}
{"authors":"田心","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>监察执法","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 14pt\">黄玉治在全国煤矿安全监管监察执法工作座谈会上强调<span lang=\"EN-US\">:\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">以党的十九大精神为指引</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri\">推动煤矿安全监管监察执法工作再上新台阶</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Calibri; FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\">\n   <st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"14\" month=\"12\" year=\"2017\">\n    <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">12</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">月<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">14</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">日</span></span></span></span>\n   </st1:chsdate><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">至<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">15</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">日，全国煤矿安全监管监察执法工作座谈会在北京召开。国家安全监管总局副局长、国家煤矿安监局局长黄玉治出席会议并讲话。国家煤矿安监局副局长李万疆主持会议并进行会议总结。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">黄玉治指出，近年来煤矿安全监管监察执法工作取得明显进展，<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">安全”体检”和大检查工作扎实推进，<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">执法规范化建设不断加强，<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">执法处罚力度不断加大，<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">执法方式更加多样灵活，<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">执法监督工作有序开展，<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">执法信息化建设稳步推进，<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">实现了煤矿安全生产形势持续稳定好转。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n            <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">黄玉治强调，各级煤矿安全监管监察部门要深入学习贯彻党的十九大精神，<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">将十九大战略部署转化为指导推进煤矿安全生产工作的具体举措，推动执法工作再上新台阶。同时，<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">也要清醒认识新时代煤矿安全监管监察执法工作面临的形势，解决监管监察执法不适应、不到位等问题。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">黄玉治要求，下一步要以习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想为指导，深入学习贯彻党的十九大精神和习近平总书记、李克强总理等中央领导同志关于安全生产工作的重要指示批示精神，坚持安全发展，着力推进严格、规范、公正、文明执法，着力推进执法基础能力建设，着力推进执法规范化、专业化、信息化，进一步提高执法质量和水平，努力实现事故总量、较大事故、重特大事故、百万吨死亡率“四下降”，为决胜全面建成小康社会、实现人民群众对美好生活的向往作出积极贡献。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p></font>\n</div>","createTime":1518425397721,"modules":[],"pubSource":"煤矿安监局安全监察司","pubTime":1513267200000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"黄玉治在全国煤矿安全监管监察执法工作座谈会上强调","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_6486/2017/1215/299797/content_299797.htm"}
