mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">（第三批）的通知</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">安监总煤行<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">﹝<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">2018<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">﹞<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">20<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">号<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n          <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">各产煤省、自治区、直辖市及新疆生产建设兵团煤炭行业管理部门、煤矿安全监管部门，各省级煤矿安全监察局，司法部直属煤矿管理局，有关中央企业：<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">按照《煤矿安全生产标准化考核定级办法（试行）》（煤安监行管〔<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2017</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">〕<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">5</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">号）规定，经资料审查、现场检查、网上公示，确认开滦（集团）有限责任公司钱家营矿业分公司等<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">30</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">处煤矿（名单附后）为一级安全生产标准化煤矿，现予以公布。自公布之日起生效，有效期<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">3</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n             <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">根据国家安全监管总局、国家煤矿安监局、国家发展改革委、国家能源局联合印发的《关于大力推进煤矿安全生产标准化建设工作的通知》（安监总煤行〔<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2017</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">〕<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">59</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">号）和《关于明确煤炭产能置换和生产能力核定工作中有关事项的通知》（发改办运行〔<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2017</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">〕<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1448</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">号）有关规定，以及《国家煤矿安全监察局局长办公会议纪要》（<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2018</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年第<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">3</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">号）有关要求，上述<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">30</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">处煤矿在标准化等级有效期内享受以下激励政策：<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n                   <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">一、在全国性或区域性调整、实施减量化生产措施时，原则上不纳入减量化生产煤矿范围。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">二、在地方政府因其他煤矿发生事故采取区域政策性停产措施时，原则上不纳入停产范围。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">三、生产能力核增时，产能置换比例不小于核增产能的<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">100%</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">四、大型煤矿核增生产能力时，核定后的服务年限原则上不少于<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">20</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">五、停产后复产验收时，优先进行复产验收。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">六、在安全生产许可证有效期届满时，符合相关条件的，可以直接办理延期手续。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">七、银行、证券、保险、担保等主管部门作为对煤矿企业信用评级重要参考依据。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">八、各级煤矿安全监管监察部门适当减少检查频次（已公布确定的第一批、第二批一级安全生产标准化煤矿同样适用）。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">附件：<a href=\"http://www.chinasafety.gov.cn/newpage/newfiles/20180126-1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">一级安全生产标准化煤矿名单（第三批）</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">国家安全监管总局<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">国家煤矿安监局<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2018</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">1</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">26</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n          <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p></font>\n</div>","createTime":1518425399147,"modules":[],"pubSource":"煤矿安监局行业安全基础管理指导司","pubTime":1516896000000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"国家安全监管总局","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5475/2018/0126/300926/content_300926.htm"}
{"authors":"李静","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>重要通知","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">国家煤矿安监局办公室关于转发</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \r\n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /-->\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">《河南省煤矿瓦斯防治补充规定》的通知</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">煤安监司函办<span lang=\"EN-US\">[2017]14号<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">各产煤省、自治区、直辖市及新疆生产建设兵团煤炭行业管理部门、煤矿安全监管部门，各省级煤矿安全监察局，司法部直属煤矿管理局，各有关中央企业：<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">现将河南煤矿安全监察局、河南省煤炭工业管理办公室制定的《河南省煤矿瓦斯防治补充规定》转发给你们，供学习借鉴。各单位要结合实际，进一步强化落实煤矿瓦斯综合防治措施，坚决防范和遏制煤矿瓦斯事故，促进全国煤矿安全生产形势持续稳定好转。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\"> \n      <o:p></o:p></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">国家煤矿安监局办公室<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2017</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">4</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">月<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">21</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">日<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\"> \n           <o:p></o:p></font></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">河南省煤矿瓦斯防治补充规定</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">为切实加强煤矿瓦斯防治工作，有效防范和坚决遏制煤矿重特大事故，现就与煤与瓦斯突出矿井相邻开采同一煤层经过鉴定为非突出的煤矿，提出以下十条要求，凡未落实的，以及与煤与瓦斯突出矿井相邻开采同一煤层既未鉴定也未按突出矿井管理的，一律停止采掘作业。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">一、必须加强对断层、褶曲、陷落柱、煤层厚度及倾角变化等煤层产状变化带和地质构造异常区的探查，及时掌握掘进、回采区域内的地质情况，掘进、回采前按规定编制掘进地质说明书和回采地质说明书，由矿井总工程师组织会审，矿长签字确认，指导安全掘进和回采。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">二、出现煤岩瓦斯涌出异常，有卡钻、顶钻、喷孔等动力现象，必须立即停止采掘作业，直接升级为煤与瓦斯突出矿井。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">三、煤巷、半煤岩巷掘进和采煤工作面，必须执行局部综合防突措施，预测有突出危险时，必须立即停止采掘作业，矿井直接升级为煤与瓦斯突出矿井。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">四、掘进工作面绝对瓦斯涌出量大于<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">3m3/min</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">，采煤工作面绝对瓦斯涌出量大于<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">5m3/min</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">，必须停止掘进、回采，实施瓦斯抽放。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n         <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">五、岩巷掘进必须按《防治煤与瓦斯突出规定》制定并落实防止误揭煤层措施，坚持先探后掘。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">六、井巷揭煤和过煤门，必须按《防治煤与瓦斯突出规定》制定、落实揭煤和过煤门防突措施。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">七、必须测定矿井瓦斯基础参数，编制瓦斯地质图，瓦斯地质图必须包含瓦斯压力、含量、涌出量等值线。地方煤矿聘请专家或中介机构编制瓦斯地质图，由上一级公司主要负责人牵头组织专家审查、批复；骨干企业所属煤矿瓦斯地质图由骨干企业总工程师组织专家审查、批复。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">八、必须建立井下临时瓦斯抽采系统，并实现瓦斯抽采在线监测。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">九、必须按照煤与瓦斯突出矿井建立、执行瓦斯检查制度，配足专业技术人员和防突、瓦斯检查等特种作业人员。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">十、严禁任何<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">个工作面之间串联通风。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <o:p>\n     <font face=\"Calibri\">&nbsp;</font>\n    </o:p></span></p></font>\n</div>","createTime":1518425399180,"modules":[],"pubSource":"煤矿安监局办公室","pubTime":1493136000000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"国家煤矿安监局办公室关于转发","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5476/2017/0426/287663/content_287663.htm"}
{"authors":"李静","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>基础管理","content":"<td class=\"font14 lineHeight25\" id=\"artibody\"><font face=\"宋体\"> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">国家煤矿安监局办公室关于征求</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">《煤矿安全生产标准化基本要求及评分方法</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">（征求意见稿）》意见的函</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18pt\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312\">煤安监司函办〔<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016〕<span lang=\"EN-US\">26号<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">各产煤省、自治区、直辖市及新疆生产建设兵团煤矿安全质量标准化工作主管部门，各省级煤矿安全监察局：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">国家煤矿安监局在《煤矿安全质量标准化基本要求及评分方法（试行）》基础上，组织制定了《煤矿安全生产标准化基本要求及评分方法（征求意见稿）》，现印发你们征求意见（可从国家安全监管总局网站“征求意见”栏目下载，网址：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">www.chinasafety.gov.cn</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">）。请认真组织研究，并于\n      <st1:chsdate year=\"2016\" month=\"10\" day=\"20\" islunardate=\"False\" isrocdate=\"False\" w:st=\"on\">\n       <span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2016</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">10</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">20</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">日前</span></span></span></span></span></span>\n      </st1:chsdate><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">将书面意见连同电子版一并反馈国家煤矿安监局行业管理司。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n        <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">联系人及电话：梁子荣；<font face=\"Times New Roman\"> </font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">电话：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">010-64464789</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">、<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">64464294</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">（传真）；电子信箱：<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">liangzr@chinasafety.gov.cn</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n            <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">附件：<a href=\"files_founder_2181914966/117568.doc\" target=\"_blank\">煤矿安全生产标准化基本要求及评分方法</a>&nbsp; </span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">国家煤矿安监局办公室<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 19pt; TEXT-ALIGN: right; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" align=\"right\">\n   <st1:chsdate year=\"2016\" month=\"9\" day=\"26\" islunardate=\"False\" isrocdate=\"False\" w:st=\"on\">\n    <span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2016</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">年<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">9</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">26</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-hansi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">日</span></span></span></span></span></span>\n   </st1:chsdate></p></font></td>","createTime":1518425399211,"modules":[],"pubSource":"煤矿安监局办公室","pubTime":1474992000000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"国家煤矿安监局办公室关于征求","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_6489/2016/0928/294666/content_294666.htm"}
{"authors":"刘森","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>煤矿安全生产许可","content":"<td class=\"font11pt lineHeight25\" id=\"artibody\"> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">近期，经国家煤矿安监局审查：山西三交一号煤矿，内蒙古石拉乌素煤矿，陕西沙梁煤矿、招贤煤矿，新疆大南湖矿区西区五号煤矿、阿艾矿区大平滩煤矿、准东西黑山矿区红沙泉一号露天煤矿一期工程、淖毛湖矿区白石湖露天煤矿一期工程等<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">8</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">个煤矿建设项目开采技术条件勘查符合有关要求，基本满足设计需要；建设单位主体企业具有相应灾害类型煤矿安全管理的经验和业绩。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \r\n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /-->\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p><font face=\"宋体\"></font></td>","createTime":1518425399243,"modules":[],"pubSource":"安全监管总局人事司（宣教办","pubTime":1496592000000,"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"8个煤矿建设项目符合安全核准要求","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5480/2017/0605/289411/content_289411.htm"}
{"authors":"刘森","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>要闻","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\"> </font></span></p>\n  <table style=\"WIDTH: 549px; HEIGHT: 414px\" id=\"table2\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"5\" cellpadding=\"5\" width=\"549\" align=\"center\"> \n   <tbody> \n    <tr> \n     <td><img src=\"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5474/2017/0927/295373/files_founder_2153232117/2985520396.jpg\"></td>\n    </tr> \n    <tr> \n     <td><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\" lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;9<span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; COLOR: blue; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\">27日，国家安监总局、国家煤监局和黑龙江省政府在哈尔滨市联合召开黑龙江省煤矿安全生产警示教育会。<font color=\"#0000ff\" face=\"楷体_GB2312\"></font></span></span></span></td>\n    </tr>\n   </tbody>\n  </table><p></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">9</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">月<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">27</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">日，国家安监总局、国家煤监局和黑龙江省政府在哈尔滨市联合召开黑龙江省煤矿安全生产警示教育会，深刻吸取近年来煤矿事故教训，分析煤矿安全生产存在问题和面临形势，研究加强和改进煤矿安全生产工作措施，有效防范和坚决遏制重特大事故，为党的十九大胜利召开营造稳定的安全生产环境。国家安监总局副局长、国家煤监局局长黄玉治和黑龙江省副省长胡亚枫出席会议并讲话，国家煤监局副局长杨富主持会议。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n        <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">黄玉治指出，近年来黑龙江煤矿安全生产工作取得了积极进展<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">,</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">但安全形势十分严峻，重大事故时有发生，在安全红线意识、禁止违法违规行为、落实企业主体责任、治理重大灾害、淘汰落后产能等方面存在问题和挑战。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">黄玉治强调，下一步黑龙江煤矿安全生产工作要坚持目标导向和问题导向，深入开展安全大检查和安全“体检”工作；着力推进瓦斯、水害等重大灾害治理，严防大矿发生大事故；大力推进煤矿资源整合和落后产能淘汰退出工作，严格控制新增产能，加快关闭不具备安全生产条件的小煤矿；扎实推进煤矿安全基础建设，推进机械化、自动化改造和“一优三减”；开展《规程》对标执法，严厉打击超层越界等违法开采行为；严格事故调查和责任追究，强化警示教育；做好保供应期间煤矿安全生产工作，严格复工复产验收。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">胡亚枫要求，真正吸取事故教训，着力解决煤矿安全生产存在的突出问题，对省委省政府决定开展煤矿安全生产专项整治进行动员部署，从严要求。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">会上，播放了近期重大煤矿事故警示教育片，省级有关部门、有关产煤地市政府、煤矿企业主要负责人就吸取事故教训做了发言。</span></p><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\"> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" sizcache03544498514841203=\"3\" sizset=\"40\" sizcache02322384791264719=\"3\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">（安全监管总局通信信息中心<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\"> 李振营</font><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">/</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast\">摄）<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n         <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n    <o:p></o:p></span></span></font>\n</div>","createTime":1518425399266,"modules":[],"pubSource":"煤矿安监局办公室","pubTime":1506441600000,"region":["黑龙江省"],"sourceName":"国家煤矿安全监察局","sourceType":1,"title":"国家安监总局、国家煤监局和黑龙江省政府联合召开黑龙江省煤矿安全生产警示教育会","url":"http://www.chinacoal-safety.gov.cn/Contents/Channel_5474/2017/0927/295373/content_295373.htm"}
