font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年煤炭行业标准制修订</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">项目计划的通知</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 20pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt\">安监总煤装函〔<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017〕<span lang=\"EN-US\">57号<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">中国煤炭工业协会，全国煤炭标准化技术委员会、煤炭行业煤矿专用设备标准化技术委员会、煤炭行业煤矿安全标准化技术委员会：<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">现将《煤矿水中铜、铅、锌、镉、锰的测定》等<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">23</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">项<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2017</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年煤炭行业标准制修订项目计划（详见附件）下达给你们，请抓紧组织实施，并就有关要求通知如下：<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n         <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">一、按照《安全生产标准制修订工作细则》（国家安全监管总局令第<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">9</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">号）要求，制定工作计划，成立标准起草小组，明确专人负责，按期完成标准项目的制修订工作。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">二、切实加强对煤炭行业标准起草工作的管理，跟踪督促检查标准项目制修订工作进展情况，及时审查，保证标准制修订质量。<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">附件：<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><a href=\"files_founder_1025724828/6737210.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Calibri\">2017</font><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin\">年煤炭行业标准制修订项目计划<span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\"><font face=\"Calibri\">&nbsp;<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n            <o:p></o:p></span></font></span></span></span></a></font></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 16pt\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE