{"authors":"李振营","channel":"首页>煤矿安全监察>公告公文","content":"<div class=\"display_nr pages_content\">\n <font face=\"宋体\"> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">国家煤矿安监局办公室关于报送<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017年度<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \r\n\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" /-->\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 20pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">煤矿安全培训考核工作总结材料的通知<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></b></p> <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\">煤安监司函办〔<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017〕<span lang=\"EN-US\">58号<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n       <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">各产煤省、自治区、直辖市及新疆生产建设兵团煤矿安全培训主管部门，有关涉煤中央企业：<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n     <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">请各单位认真汇总<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017年度煤矿“三项岗位人员”安全培训考核发证监督检查情况，总结煤矿安全培训工作经验，分析存在的主要问题，提出加强和改进煤矿安全培训工作的意见建议，形成总结报告，并填报<span lang=\"EN-US\">2017年<span lang=\"EN-US\">1-10月煤矿“三项岗位人员”安全培训情况和<span lang=\"EN-US\">11-12月计划培训人数、煤矿主要负责人和安全生产管理人员考核情况统计表（附件<span lang=\"EN-US\">1、<span lang=\"EN-US\">2、<span lang=\"EN-US\">3，有关涉煤中央企业不填），于<span lang=\"EN-US\">12月<span lang=\"EN-US\">10日前将总结报告及表格以传真和电子邮件方式报送至国家煤矿安监局行业管理司（报表格式电子版在国家煤矿安全监察局政府网站“公告公文”栏目下载）。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n              <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">联系人及电话：潘霄，<span lang=\"EN-US\">010-64464064（带传真）；<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 12pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-fareast\">电子邮箱：<span lang=\"EN-US\">panx@chinasafety.gov.cn。<span lang=\"EN-US\">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></span></span></p> <p style=\"LINE-